==Swedish==
===Etymology===
From [[ljud]] (''[[sound]]'') + [[-lös]] (''suffix to denote lack; [[-less]]'') + [[-het#Swedish|-het]] (''noun of state suffix; [[-ness]]'') 

===Noun===
'''ljudlöshet'''

#[[noiselessness]] ''or'' [[soundlessness]]; the state of being [[silent]]

